OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779657075
OL,3,CMotorist shot by police after car
OL,4,Cdriven 'directly at officers' in Bury
OL,6,FA motorist was shot by police in Bury
OL,7,Fafter driving directly at officers
OL,8,Fwhile attempting to get away, police
OL,9,Fhave said.
OL,11,FGreater Manchester Police (GMP) said
OL,12,Fofficers attempted to stop a vehicle
OL,13,Fon Bury New Road in Whitefield at 3pm
OL,14,Fon Friday.
OL,16,FThe force said "the car failed to stop
OL,17,Fand drove directly at our officers to
OL,18,Fget away" and a shot was fired by a
OL,19,Ffirearms officer.
OL,26,@xD@POUzD@IO]
