FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779657075
OL,3,CMotorist shot by police after car
OL,4,Cdriven 'directly at officers' in Bury
OL,6,FThe driver of the car was taken to
OL,7,Fhospital for an injury to his arm,
OL,8,Fwhich has been described as neither
OL,9,Flife threatening nor life changing.
OL,11,FNo police officers were injured in the
OL,12,Fincident and investigations are
OL,13,Fongoing, police said.
OL,15,FGMP said the incident has been
OL,16,Freferred to the Independent Office for
OL,17,FPolice Conduct "as per standard
OL,18,Fprocedure".
OL,26,@yD@POUzD@JO]
