OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779657075
OL,3,CMotorist shot by police after car
OL,4,Cdriven 'directly at officers' in Bury
OL,6,FA 20-year-old white British man has
OL,7,Fbeen arrested on suspicion of being
OL,8,Fconcerned in the supply of class A
OL,9,Fdrugs.
OL,11,FDetective Superintendent Joe Harrop,
OL,12,Ffrom GMP's serious crime division,
OL,13,Fsaid: "We know people in the area will
OL,14,Fbe concerned by what has happened and
OL,15,Fthe visible increase in police
OL,16,Fofficers in the local area as our
OL,17,Finvestigations continue.
OL,26,@uD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
