OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779657075
OL,3,CMotorist shot by police after car
OL,4,Cdriven 'directly at officers' in Bury
OL,6,F"Thankfully no members of the wider
OL,7,Fpublic, or officers were harmed in the
OL,8,Fincident this afternoon and we thank
OL,9,Fpeople for their patience while we
OL,10,Fremain at the scene.
OL,12,F"Should anyone have any concerns,
OL,13,Fplease speak with our officers who are
OL,14,Fout in the local area, they are there
OL,15,Fto listen and assist where possible."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@eO]
